      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/2/01/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/2/01/01_shrAvaNyAm_paurNamAsyAM_shr.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;01 श्रावण्याम् पौर्णमास्यां श्रवणाकर्म ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;श्रावण्यां पौर्णमास्यां श्रवणाकर्म १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/oldenberg/2/01/01_shrAvaNyAm_paurNamAsyAM_shr.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;1 &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; . On the full moon day of the Śrāvaṇa month the Śrāvaṇa ceremony (is performed).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;मूलम्&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/mUlam/2/01/01_shrAvaNyAm_paurNamAsyAM_shr.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;मूलम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;श्रावण्यां पौर्णमास्यां श्रवणाकर्म १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/2/01/02_axatasaktUnAn_navankalasham.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;02 अक्षतसक्तूनान् नवङ्कलशम् पूरयित्वा ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अक्षतसक्तूनां नवङ्कलशं पूरयित्वा दर्वीञ्च बलिहरणीं नवे शिक्ये निदधाति २&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/oldenberg/2/01/02_axatasaktUnAn_navankalasham.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol start=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Having filled a new jug with flour of fried barley, he lays (this jug) and a spoon for offering the Balis on new strings of a carrying pole (and thus suspends them).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;मूलम्&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/mUlam/2/01/02_axatasaktUnAn_navankalasham.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;मूलम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अक्षतसक्तूनां नवङ्कलशं पूरयित्वा दर्वीञ्च बलिहरणीं नवे शिक्ये निदधाति २&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०२</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/2/02/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/2/02/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/2/02/01_AshvayujyAmAshvayujIkarma.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;01 आश्वयुज्यामाश्वयुजीकर्म ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;आश्वयुज्यामाश्वयुजीकर्म १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/oldenberg/2/02/01_AshvayujyAmAshvayujIkarma.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;On the full moon day of Āśvayuja the Āśvayujī ceremony (is performed).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;मूलम्&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/mUlam/2/02/01_AshvayujyAmAshvayujIkarma.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;मूलम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;आश्वयुज्यामाश्वयुजीकर्म १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/2/02/02_niveshanamalankRtya_snAtAH_.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;02 निवेशनमलङ्कृत्य स्नाताः शुचिवाससः ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;निवेशनमलङ्कृत्य स्नाताः शुचिवाससः पशुपतये स्थालीपाकं निरुप्य जुहुयुः पशुपतये शिवाय शङ्कराय पृषातकाय स्वाहेति २&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/oldenberg/2/02/02_niveshanamalankRtya_snAtAH_.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;2 &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; . Having adorned the house, having bathed and put on clean garments, they should pour out a mess of cooked food for Paśupati, and should sacrifice it with (the formula), To Paśupati, to Śiva, to Śaṃkara, to Pṛṣātaka svāhā!&#39;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
