ummary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;एकस्यां वा २&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/oldenberg/2/04/02_ekasyAM_vA.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;2 &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:2&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:2&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; . Or on one (of these days).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;मूलम्&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/mUlam/2/04/02_ekasyAM_vA.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;मूलम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;एकस्यां वा २&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/2/04/03_pUrvedyuH_pitRbhyo_dadyAt.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;03 पूर्वेद्युः पितृभ्यो दद्यात् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;पूर्वेद्युः पितृभ्यो दद्यात् ३&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०५</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/2/05/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/sarva-prastutiH/2/05/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/2/05/01_aparedyuranvaShTakyam.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;01 अपरेद्युरन्वष्टक्यम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अपरेद्युरन्वष्टक्यम् १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/oldenberg/2/05/01_aparedyuranvaShTakyam.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;On the following day the Anvaṣṭakya (i.e. the ceremony following the Aṣṭakā, is performed).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;मूलम्&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/mUlam/2/05/01_aparedyuranvaShTakyam.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;मूलम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अपरेद्युरन्वष्टक्यम् १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/2/05/02_tasyaiva_mAMsasya_prakalpya.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;02 तस्यैव मांसस्य प्रकल्प्य ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;तस्यैव मांसस्य प्रकल्प्य दक्षिणाप्रवणेऽग्निमुपसमाधाय परिश्रित्योत्तरतः परिश्रितस्य द्वारं कृत्वा समूलं बर्हिस्त्रिरपसलैरविधून्वन्परिस्तीर्य हवींष्यासादयेदोदनं कृसरं पायसं दधिमन्थान्मधुमन्थांश्च २&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/oldenberg/2/05/02_tasyaiva_mAMsasya_prakalpya.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;2 &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; . Having prepared (a portion) of that same meat, having established the fire on a surface inclined towards the south, having fenced it in, and made a door on the north side of the enclosure, having strewn round (the fire) three times sacrificial grass with its roots, without tossing it, turning the left side towards the fire, he should put down the things to be offered, boiled rice, boiled rice with sesamum seeds, rice-milk, meal-pap with curds, and meal-pap with honey.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०६</title>
