      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/vishvAsa-prastutiH/2/06/01_rathamAroxyannAnA_pANibhyA~.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;01 रथमारोक्ष्यन्नाना पाणिभ्याञ् चक्रे ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;रथमारोक्ष्यन्नाना पाणिभ्यां चक्रे अभिमृशेत् अहन्ते पूर्वं पादावालभेद्बृहद्रथन्तरे ते चक्रे १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;Oldenberg&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/oldenberg/2/06/01_rathamAroxyannAnA_pANibhyA~.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Oldenberg ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;1 &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; . When going to mount a chariot he should touch the wheels with his two hands separately with (the words), &amp;lsquo;I touch thy two fore-feet. Thy two wheels are the Bṛhat and the Rathantara (Sāmans).&amp;rsquo;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;मूलम्&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_Rk/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/sUtram/AshvalAyanaH/gRhyam/mUlam/2/06/01_rathamAroxyannAnA_pANibhyA~.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;मूलम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;रथमारोक्ष्यन्नाना पाणिभ्यां चक्रे अभिमृशेत् अहन्ते पूर्वं पादावालभेद्बृहद्रथन्तरे ते चक्रे १&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
